      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/turkey-central-bank-lifts-rates-once-again-nears-end-of-cycle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行连续第七次加息，作为抑制未来几个月通胀率加速至 70% 努力的一部分。]]></description>
