    <item>
      <title>迈克尔·普拉特 (Michael Platt) 的 BlueCrest 在与英国就薪酬计划展开的税务斗争中败诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/michael-platt-s-bluecrest-loses-tax-fight-with-uk-over-pay-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈克尔·普拉特 (Michael Platt) 的 BlueCrest 资本管理公司 (BlueCrest Capital Management) 在与英国当局就一项旨在留住该基金部分高级交易员的薪酬计划的税收待遇问题上输掉了大部分法律诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/michael-platt-s-bluecrest-loses-tax-fight-with-uk-over-pay-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 10:57:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士宝盛集团降级、数十亿欧元索赔显示信号蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/julius-baer-outlook-cut-to-negative-by-moody-s-on-governance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自全球金融危机以来欧洲最大规模的房地产崩盘之一，在穆迪下调瑞士宝盛集团有限公司信贷前景以及中东投资者提出超过 10 亿欧元（合 11 亿美元）索赔后，开始造成更广泛的痛苦。雷内·本科 (Rene Benko) 的西尼亚 (Signa) 集团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/julius-baer-outlook-cut-to-negative-by-moody-s-on-governance</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 07:02:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员指责零日期权是标普下跌的罪魁祸首</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/fingers-point-at-vilified-zero-day-options-to-explain-stock-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年最热门的衍生品交易，或许也是最具争议性的衍生品交易，在 2023 年最后一次成为众人瞩目的焦点，市场观察人士将零日期权视为周三美国股市反弹结束暴跌的罪魁祸首。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/fingers-point-at-vilified-zero-day-options-to-explain-stock-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 01:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>红海风险打压美国创纪录产量，油价稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在连续三天上涨后企稳，交易员权衡美国产量激增与胡塞武装袭击关键水道船只的持续威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 00:07:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
